What is rest assured?
- It is a java library to test Rest APIs

How do you use it?
- We create a request and send it to the API and get the response
- Then we write our tests for the response

How do you create a request?
- .given() -> Preparation(Token, Request Body, parameters, cookies)
         .when() -> To send the request(Request method, request url)
                .then() -> Response(Response body, tests, extract data, set local or global variables)